{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018u5AipcLP84uUVQTRecjgU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WQnw99Z5jpdRvAuX17LhEY","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/26-e8ee23c/tasks/task-06.md","content":"# Task 06: Run full evaluation and verify all fixes\n\n## Summary\n\nRun the title-loop evaluation harness to verify all 16 generated-file failures are fixed with no regressions on real files.\n\n## Dependencies\n\nTasks 01-05 must all be completed first.\n\n## Files to modify\n\n- `tools/title-loop/docs/iter.txt` (update with iteration 27 results)\n\n## Changes\n\n### Step 1: Run the evaluation harness\n\n```bash\ncd tools/title-loop && python title-loop.py\n```\n\n### Step 2: Verify results\n\nCheck the output for:\n1. **All 11 real files pass** (no regressions from 100% real accuracy)\n2. **All 16 generated-file failures are fixed:**\n   - Pattern A (5): Corrupted spillover — title absent → now extracted correctly\n   - Pattern B (2): Heavy digit corruption → OCR fully repaired, title extracted\n   - Pattern C (3): Partial corruption → OCR fully repaired, correct title wins\n   - Pattern D (3): Section header before title → first-after-preamble bonus pushes title above threshold\n   - Pattern E (1): Multi-line title truncated → `LEMON HERB ROASTED VEGETABLES` merged\n   - Pattern F (2): Mid-recipe page start → correctly detected as title-absent\n\n### Step 3: Handle partial fixes\n\nIf some failures persist:\n1. Check which patterns still fail\n2. Review the specific test case output to understand why\n3. Iterate on the relevant task's fix (do NOT change other fixes)\n\n### Step 4: Edge case verification\n\nManually check the edge cases from the spec:\n- A recipe titled `\"Vegetable Soup\"` where `\"VEGETABLES\"` appears standalone → should NOT merge if preceded by 5+ word title\n- A recipe starting with `\"½ cup\"` as first ingredient but with a title on line 0 → `isTitleAbsentPage` should NOT fire\n- Single-word `\"SKŁADNIKI\"` at line 2 following a complete title at line 0 → should NOT merge\n- Page with body prose on lines 0-2 but valid title at position 0 → extraction must still work\n\n### Step 5: Record results\n\nUpdate `tools/title-loop/docs/iter.txt` with the iteration 27 accuracy numbers.\n\n## Verification\n\n- Combined accuracy should be ≥ 97% (fixing all 16 failures from 85.6% baseline)\n- Real file accuracy remains 100% (11/11)\n- No new failures introduced\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":363,"cache_read_input_tokens":43337,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":363},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"45df4770-9767-477d-a65f-eaa50cfc39f0","uuid":"b955dc9e-efd9-4a6c-956d-d81492e8721d"}
